If you wish to be represented, please contact your attorney or accredited representative to submit a new Form G-28 to the USCIS location where your case is pending. For more information on filing a Form G-28, please visit http://www.uscis.gov/forms/filing-your-form-g-28. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
